net.sf.jclec.mo.evaluation.fitness

Class MOFitness

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.base.AbstractFitness
      • net.sf.jclec.mo.evaluation.fitness.MOFitness
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, net.sf.jclec.IFitness, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GrEAMOFitness, HypercubeMOFitness, NSGA2MOFitness, OMOPSOMOFitness, PAESMOFitness

    public class MOFitness
extends net.sf.jclec.base.AbstractFitness
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Fitness for a multi-objective problem. It stores both the objective values for each objective function and an independent fitness value useful for the fitness assignment method required in some multi-objective strategies.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    AbstractFitness, Serialized Form
